---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Wiki
description: Browse the InspectorWiki knowledge base — articles on every aspect of property inspection.
---
<section class="section-block">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-label">Knowledge Base</span>
    <h1>Wiki</h1>
    <p>Browse articles organized by inspection topic. Each article covers systems, defects, standards, and best practices.</p>

    <div class="topic-table">
      {%- for topic in site.wikiTopics %}
      <div class="topic-table__cell">
        <span class="topic-table__num">{% if loop.index < 10 %}0{% endif %}{{ loop.index }}</span>
        <span class="topic-table__name">{{ topic }}</span>
      </div>
      {%- endfor %}
    </div>

    <h2>All Articles</h2>
    <ul class="article-list">
      {%- for article in collections.wiki %}
      <li><a href="{{ article.url }}">{{ article.data.title }}</a></li>
      {%- endfor %}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
